<div style="background:var(--loam-white);min-height:60vh">
  <div style="background:var(--loam-black);padding:64px var(--space-6) 48px">
    <div style="max-width:900px;margin:0 auto">
      <p class="eyebrow" style="margin-bottom:16px">DELIVERY</p>
      <h1 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:clamp(48px,7vw,88px);color:var(--loam-white);line-height:.95;letter-spacing:.02em">Shipping info</h1>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div style="max-width:800px;margin:0 auto;padding:64px var(--space-6);font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#E8E6E1">

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:0 0 20px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">UK Delivery</h2>
    <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:40px;font-size:14px">
      <thead>
        <tr style="background:#FFFFFF;color:#0A0A0A">
          <th style="text-align:left;padding:12px 16px;font-family:var(--font-narrow);letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:12px">SERVICE</th>
          <th style="text-align:left;padding:12px 16px;font-family:var(--font-narrow);letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:12px">DELIVERY TIME</th>
          <th style="text-align:right;padding:12px 16px;font-family:var(--font-narrow);letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:12px">COST</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5">
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;font-weight:600">Standard</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;color:#9A9A9A">3–5 working days</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;text-align:right;font-weight:600">Free on orders over £50<br><span style="color:#9A9A9A;font-weight:400">£3.99 under £50</span></td>
        </tr>
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5">
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;font-weight:600">Express</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;color:#9A9A9A">1–2 working days</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;text-align:right;font-weight:600">£6.99</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;font-weight:600">Next Day <span style="font-size:11px;background:#DAEE01;color:#0A0A0A;padding:2px 6px;font-family:var(--font-narrow);letter-spacing:.1em">ORDER BY 2PM</span></td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;color:#9A9A9A">Next working day</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;text-align:right;font-weight:600">£9.99</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:40px 0 20px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">International Delivery</h2>
    <table style="width:100%;border-collapse:collapse;margin-bottom:40px;font-size:14px">
      <thead>
        <tr style="background:#FFFFFF;color:#0A0A0A">
          <th style="text-align:left;padding:12px 16px;font-family:var(--font-narrow);letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:12px">DESTINATION</th>
          <th style="text-align:left;padding:12px 16px;font-family:var(--font-narrow);letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:12px">DELIVERY TIME</th>
          <th style="text-align:right;padding:12px 16px;font-family:var(--font-narrow);letter-spacing:.1em;font-size:12px">COST</th>
        </tr>
      </thead>
      <tbody>
        <tr style="border-bottom:1px solid #e5e5e5">
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;font-weight:600">Europe</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;color:#9A9A9A">5–10 working days</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;text-align:right;font-weight:600">£12.99</td>
        </tr>
        <tr>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;font-weight:600">Rest of World</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;color:#9A9A9A">7–14 working days</td>
          <td style="padding:14px 16px;text-align:right;font-weight:600">£18.99</td>
        </tr>
      </tbody>
    </table>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:40px 0 16px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">Processing time</h2>
    <p>Orders are processed within 1–2 working days. You will receive a dispatch confirmation email with a tracking link as soon as your order leaves our warehouse. During busy periods (new drops, sale events), processing may take up to 3 working days.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:40px 0 16px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">Duties & taxes</h2>
    <p>UK orders are inclusive of VAT. For international orders, import duties and taxes may be applied by your local customs authority. These charges are the responsibility of the recipient and are not included in the shipping fee. We have no control over these charges and cannot predict their amount.</p>

    <h2 style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.1em;margin:40px 0 16px;text-transform:uppercase;border-bottom:2px solid #2E2E2E;padding-bottom:10px">Missing or damaged orders</h2>
    <p>If your order hasn't arrived within the expected timeframe, please <a href="/pages/contact" style="color:#FFFFFF;font-weight:600">contact us</a> with your order number and we'll track it down. If your gear arrives damaged in transit, please email us a photo within 48 hours and we'll sort it immediately.</p>

    <div style="background:#FFFFFF;color:#0A0A0A;padding:28px;margin-top:48px;display:flex;align-items:flex-start;gap:20px">
      <div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:48px;color:var(--loam-neon);line-height:1">?</div>
      <div>
        <p style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;letter-spacing:.12em;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:8px">GOT A QUESTION?</p>
        <p style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(0,0,0,0.7);margin-bottom:16px">Drop us a line — we get back to every message within 48 hours.</p>
        <a href="/pages/contact" style="font-family:var(--font-narrow);font-weight:700;font-size:12px;letter-spacing:.18em;background:var(--loam-neon);color:#0A0A0A;padding:10px 20px;text-decoration:none;display:inline-block">CONTACT US</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

{% schema %}
{
  "name": "Shipping Info",
  "settings": [],
  "presets": [{ "name": "Shipping Info" }]
}
{% endschema %}
